      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts by a second analyst not involved in original model construction.",
      "rationale": "A second engineer independently reviewed boundary condition application, load application points, and post-processing macros. One minor unit inconsistency in rod modulus input was identified and corrected prior to final runs. Gradation 2 achieved."
