      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties derived from coupon testing of same Ti-6Al-4V lot; geometric inputs from CMM measurements of tested constructs.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.1 GPa) sourced from tensile coupon tests on material from the same manufacturing lot. Screw and rod dimensions verified by coordinate measuring machine on three representative samples. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
