      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production inventory. Dimensional inspection of all 11 constructs confirmed conformance to drawing tolerances. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison per ASME V&V 40 guidance. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
