      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At least two distinct loading configurations or rod diameters tested to characterize model behavior across clinically relevant parameter space.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration only. No variation in rod diameter or offset distance was included in this validation activity. This factor falls below the required Gradation 3; the shortfall is acknowledged and compensated by the high experimental sample count and inter-laboratory consistency. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
