      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model boundary conditions and loading replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry; potting depth and rod offset match measured experimental values.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 fixture geometry digitized from engineering drawings and implemented as rigid surface constraints. Potting depth (30 mm) and rod offset (35 mm) match measured experimental setup. Friction at fixture-block interface set to 0.15 consistent with UHMWPE-steel pairing. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
