      "acceptanceCriteria": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% relative to experimental mean.",
      "rationale": "Stiffness: mean experimental 187 N/mm, FEA 191 N/mm, difference 2.1%, E/uval 0.82. Yield force: mean experimental 412 N, FEA 404 N, difference 1.9%, E/uval 0.71. Force at 40 mm: mean experimental 623 N, FEA 638 N, difference 2.4%, E/uval 1.03. All three QoIs pass both acceptance criteria. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
